headline: Carrier Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Advisory
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, will release its fourth quarter 2025 earnings on Thursday, February 5, 2026 and host a conference call and webcast at 7:30 a.m. ET.
